@page "/about"

<PageTitle>NieR Reincarnation Recap - About</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">About</MudText>
<MudText Class="mb-8">Welcome to Nier Reincarnation Recap, a fan-made website to recap the mobile game Nier Reincarnation.</MudText>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Open Source</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    This website and the utility to backup your save data are completely open source under the MIT license. You
    can review the entire code-base in our <MudLink Href="https://github.com/BillyCool/NierReincarnationRecap/" Color="Color.Secondary">GitHub</MudLink> repository.<br />
</MudText>

<br />
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Technology</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" GutterBottom="true">
    NieR Reincarnation Recap is built with .NET 8 and Blazor Webassembly, using <MudLink Href="https://mudblazor.com/" Color="Color.Tertiary">MudBlazor</MudLink> components.<br />
    The API behind the scenes is powered by <MudLink Href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-functions/functions-overview" Color="Color.Tertiary">Azure Functions</MudLink>
    while the database is power by <MudLink Href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-au/products/azure-sql" Color="Color.Tertiary">Azure SQL</MudLink>.
</MudText>

